HEADWORD: Deploy
<hw>De*ploy"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp.
& p. p.</pos> <conjf>Deployed</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
