<ets>d⟦eacute⟧ployer</ets>; pref. <ets>d⟦eacute⟧</ets> =
<ets>d⟦eacute⟧s</ets> (L. <ets>dis</ets>) + <ets>ployer</ets>, equiv. to
<ets>plier</ets> to fold, fr. L. <ets>plicare</ets>. See <er>Ply</er>,
